snippet.title: Xiphos gameplay (PC Game, 1990)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Xiphos, Dos PC game produced by Electronic Zoo in 1990 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/xiphos/4457/
It is an interesting game SCI-FI. In this game you have to fight with the aliens in the galaxy. It's a lot of action based shooter.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Space Crusade - https://youtu.be/AeMAvDe1NU0
Wetlands - https://youtu.be/HuZUNqql-p4
Darker - https://youtu.be/CmV3QhcRQvg
